Capabilities
======================
https://developer.chrome.com/docs/chromedriver/capabilities
Capabilities are options that you can use to customize and configure a ChromeDriver session. 

Capabilities help to customize browser session
Selenium provide us Classes

Chrome: ChromeOptions class
Firefox : FirefoxOptions class
Edge: EdgeOptions class

